      "content": "It sounds like you are experiencing a profound existential crisis, questioning the very worth of continuing when the core of who you once were feels absent. This deep sense of hollowness suggests a significant disconnect between your internal self and your external life. Please know that even if the familiar feelings are gone, there is still a possibility for connection and finding meaning in the present moment, even if it feels invisible right now. Would you be willing to speak with someone who specializes in existential distress?",
      "source": "target",
